description:
This is a 46 minute workout called 'Free 45 Minute Spin Class |  Burn up to 600 Calories with Tabata Drills & Power Surges' from the channel Studio SWEAT onDemand.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.
